                            <comment id="12841402" author="stack" created="Thu, 4 Mar 2010 17:44:01 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for the patch Alexey Kovyrin.  I applied to trunk.  The patch is a little fragile with its hard-coding of target but its a big improvement over current condition.  Thank you.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
